        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Hey Feds, We made some changes recently in <code>haste</code>/<code>yoshi</code>/<code>generators</code>. We‚Äôll try to shed some light on the topic.</p> <h3><a class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" id="some-history"></a><a href="#some-history" aria-hidden="true" class="hash-link"><svg class="hash-link-icon" aria-hidden="true" height="16" version="1.1" viewbox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"/></svg></a>Some history</h3> <p>A few months ago we moved from <a href="https://github.com/wix/yoshi"><code>yoshi</code></a> to <a href="https://github.com/wix-private/wix-haste/blob/master/README.md"><code>haste-preset-yoshi</code></a>. <code>haste-preset-yoshi</code> is practically <code>yoshi</code>, nothing changed, same yosh...</p>]]></summary>
